scopes.name: schedule_only
scopes.explanation: Lines 2-191 comprise the full text of the Schedule to the ISDA Master Agreement, including all its Parts (1-7) and their respective provisions. The content before line 2 is exhibit labeling, and lines after 191 are signatures and execution blocks, not part of the substantive Schedule. No CSA annexes or standard pre-print Master Agreement text is included in this span.
